            Business Description
        



Euramax Holdings, which also operates under the name Almax Building Products Div, is located in Stayton, Oregon. This organization primarily operates in the Window and Door Frames business / industry within the Fabricated Metal Products sector. Euramax Holdings employs approximately 30 people at this branch location.









